{"tid":399523,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有關直播示範BinaryOption一事","createTime":"2017-09-14T04:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T15:34:40.000Z","uid":140723,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5652386e6f117b83b6461e5009a51283759e68d1","tid":399523,"uid":140723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"由於方便各位緊貼live既資訊<br />\n開左channel公佈開live時間同埋分享部分玩法<br />\n有意既可入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Biopt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBiopt&d=iLkuKafLdiqbu189Z6HAA6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7556e0b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Biopt</a>"},{"pid":"059b95497822f55a7668e6b43c9d9ee6f4f1b95e","tid":399523,"uid":57914,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"會員: 投資專家(前名稱: 半賭)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><em>教你如何賺大錢 1日10倍回報不是夢 Binary Option</em></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/399193/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/399193/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n被踢爆IQ Option係國際上出名騙局投資程式, 轉開新post再呃人<br />\n<br />\n外國人入完錢都拎唔番<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fz1ne6lc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffz1ne6lc&h=2f3b6897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要有54.5% Win rate先有錢賺, 賺完但係又拎唔到錢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>&quot;The house definitely has an edge. This particular Web site pays $71 for each successful $100 &quot;trade.&quot; If you lose, you get back $15. Let's say you make 1,000 &quot;trades&quot; and win 545 of them. Your profit is $38,695. But your 455 losses will cost you $38,675. </em></span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">In other words, you must win 54.5% of the time just to break even.</span></strong>&quot;"},{"pid":"84221a725f52f54824456e29c9d08ced7888a7e9","tid":399523,"uid":57914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"樓主推介用間IQ Option比新加